                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17251208-70-off328 t17251208-70-cd329"></join> Richard Perrin thus depos'd. As I was coming over <placeName id="t17251208-70-crimeloc330">Stepney-Fields</placeName>
